Device Statistics Registers
------------------------------
<reggrp_public_text>:
Each MAC generates a statistics vector when receiving or transmitting a frame. This vector is used for generation of the port statistics. All counters are 32 bits wide and are not reset when read. It is up to software to detect when a counter has wrapped around. When written, the counter assumes the written value.
