FEC74 correctable error counter
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
FEC corrected error counter. The FEC could detect and correct receive errors in a block. The correctable error is counted max once per FEC block (32 66-bit blocks).
------------------------------
<reg_short_dscr>:
